Uses of Package
org.sbml.jsbml.xml

Packages that use org.sbml.jsbml.xml
org.sbml.jsbml Pure Java implementation of the data structures to represent all SBML constructs. 
org.sbml.jsbml.util.compilers The classes in this package can be used to evaluate the information represented by abstract syntax trees (ASTNode objects). 
org.sbml.jsbml.xml This package provides classes and methods to deal with SBML in form of XML elements, i.e., here you can find parsers and writers for SBML and also elements to define XML nodes to be used for notes or annotations. 
org.sbml.jsbml.xml.parsers Contains classes that implement ReaderParser and/or WritingParser to read or write some specific parts of an SBML file. 
org.sbml.jsbml.xml.stax Contains classes that use the Streaming API for XML (StAX) to read or write an SBML file.
